<section class="module-small" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-11 col-md-10">
                <h2 class="module-title font-alt">What is BrAPI?</h2>
                <div class="module-subtitle font-serif large-text">
                    The Breeding API (BrAPI) project is an effort to enable interoperability among plant breeding databases. BrAPI is a standardized RESTful web service API specification for communicating plant breeding data. This community driven standard is free to be
                    used by anyone interested in plant breeding data management.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

